<h2>Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>The maximum video length depends on the type of presentation:
<ul>
    <li>Keynote presentation: 15 minutes</li>
    <li>Oral presentation: 5 minutes</li>
    <li>Poster pitch presentation: 1 minutes</li>
</ul>
<li>We prefer you to be visible in the video.</li>
<li>Record your video in the highest possible resolution with a maximum file size of 500 MB</li>
<li>Please use the number of your presentation/poster to label your file</li>
<li>For harmonization purposes, we kindly ask that you use the cover slide template (insert file) for your presentation.</li>
<li>Please send us your recording in .mp4 format.</li>
</ul>

