<h2>Besides the technical aspects described above, please consider the following</h2>
<ul>
<li>Make sure your camera is stable.</li>
<li>Avoid using copyright protected elements.</li>
<li>Take your time. Make sure you speak clearly, with intonation and engagement.</li>
<li>Make eye contact. Win the staring contest with your camera.</li>
<li>Make sure your presentation stays visible and is not obstructed by your headshot.</li>
<li>Avoid surrounding noises and echos. We recommend using a microphone.</li>
<li>Find natural light and try to avoid backlight. We want to be able to see you.</li>
